<plot>When I grow up I want to be a firefighter," is a phrase heard from children throughout the world. Children are drawn to the trucks, uniforms, equipment, noisy siren and heroic figures of firefighters. In this first episode, the Ki-Kids learn what a firefighter does besides put out fires. And they learn the importance of helping each other - all in the context of an entertaining story with Mr. K as their guide so they can learn both Spanish and English.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?290643</url></doc>
